{"tid":1483240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】維園要人 銅鑼灣入維園方法","createTime":"2019-08-18T11:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T12:26:11.000Z","uid":100811,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d4d99a39394a85c8fe1467531aae9a164422c0","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係銅鑼灣sogo塞撚咗兩個鐘</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYSsCWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYSsCWn.png&h=93428edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾經銅鑼灣站搭去天后 <br />\n十分十分鬆動 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXxPRgR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXxPRgR.png&h=bbccdd13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">維園好吉銅鑼灣塞撚到仆街大家唔好係SOGO 鳩塞 <br />\n因為ikea 係出口來嫁 維園出的人係一路出緊來 <br />\n完全無路畀sogo 的人入維園<br />\n維園好吉 經天后入呀 唔好塞係到呀！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8c7cbf0e0a552df40ad181c4ed67a3676fe34442","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8d4d99a39394a85c8fe1467531aae9a164422c0","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係銅鑼灣sogo塞撚咗兩個鐘</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYSsCWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYSsCWn.png&h=93428edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾經銅鑼灣站搭去天后 <br />\n十分十分鬆動 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXxPRgR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXxPRgR.png&h=bbccdd13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">維園好吉銅鑼灣塞撚到仆街大家唔好係SOGO 鳩塞 <br />\n因為ikea 係出口來嫁 維園出的人係一路出緊來 <br />\n完全無路畀sogo 的人入維園<br />\n維園好吉 經天后入呀 唔好塞係到呀！</span></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59395028d7559ccda1203060f402f952fa9b8604","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f60e4cb14fb2334c2ec5c8fbbfa3979b0c41a1d","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90cb1c1a845d74e44adad5a6643426c704212bdb","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"460ef6c6e31bdc112a5ef1dcf72beee879cbfd7b","tid":1483240,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4912aef3c40e21c7818a087982738dae2234017e","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d9643e7875a1916bd5155c646e3dcec97416e04","tid":1483240,"uid":170297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"除左不要入中聯辦，入維園都好重要"},{"pid":"16cf76c2b6cddf7e88aeca4c132e93770cbd8628","tid":1483240,"uid":177510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c458bae52cc3c2b0dff1da3f3b3570f4ff1cf1","tid":1483240,"uid":170297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"除左不要入中聯辦，入維園都好重要"},{"pid":"a1f928526b60fc57fd829453946ea54a7e010270","tid":1483240,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df196c6c08d80313566163c9cf483fed0ba94669","tid":1483240,"uid":284035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"42dc12fcd38b73dec0c000aca